plot: Ross finds out his ex-wife is pregnant. Rachel returns her engagement ring to Barry. Monica becomes stressed when her and Ross's parents come to visit.

After learning the shocking news that his lesbian ex-wife, Carol, is pregnant with his child, Ross is even more shocked to find out that her and her lesbian lover will not use his last name in their child's title. Rachel apprehensively returns her engagement ring to her ex-fiancé Barry after leaving him at the altar. Monica prepares dinner for her parents and Ross, whom their parents favor over her.—gdubs-41348

Ross finds out that his ex-wife Carol is pregnant with his child. He's stunned to learn she wants to give the baby her and her lesbian lovers last name.
